established = 1 January 1980\n| focus = \n| staff = \n| president = Engg. Kazi Abdul Wahid <ref name=\"iau.edu.bd\">https://iau.edu.bd/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/dhirpur-islamia-fazil-fdhaka-6874.pdf</ref>\n| chairman = \n| head_label = \n| head = \n| faculty = \n| adjunct_faculty = \n| footnotes = EIIN: \u09e7\u09e7\u09e7\u09e8\u09eb\u09e6  <br/> Mobile: 01704-511940 <br/> E-mail: dhipurifm@gmail.com <ref>{{cite web |url= https://www.sohopathi.com/dhipur-islamia-fazil-madrasah/ |title= Dhipur Islamia Fazil Madrasah |last= |first= |date= |website= Sohopathi.com |publisher= |access-date= 3 November 2019 |quote=}}</ref>\n}}\n'''Dhipur Islamia Fazil Madrasah''' is a Fazil Madrasa of [[Tongibari Upazila|Tongibari]], [[Munshiganj District|Munshiganj]]. Since its inception, the institution has been spreading education among the students of this area. It is affiliated to [[Islamic University, Kushtia|Islamic university, Kushtia]] and [[Islamic Arabic University|Islamic Arabic university, Dhaka]]. Madrasa gets MPO on 1 January 1985.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.emis.gov.bd:2020/mpo/page_search_enlisting_final.aspx|title=Mpo Done and Published|last=|first=|date=|website=EMIS, Directorate of Secondary and Higher Education|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191103171329/http://www.emis.gov.bd:2020/mpo/page_search_enlisting_final.aspx|archive-date=3 November 2019|access-date=3 November 2019}}</ref>\n\n== History ==\nThe madrasa was first established in Marialoy. Later it is moved to its current location. It is located in the village of Dhipur, near Tongi Bari upazila (2&nbsp;km south). The madrasa was established in 1980. <ref name=\":0\">{{Cite web|url=http://dhipurup.munshiganj.gov.bd/site/education_institute/e6f8a9d0-2015-11e7-8f57-286ed488c766/%E0%A6%A7%E0%A7%80%E0%A6%AA%E0%A7%81%E0%A6%B0%20%E0%A6%87%E0%A6%B8%E0%A6%B2%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%AE%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%AF%E0%A6%BC%E0%A6%BE%20%E0%A6%AB%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%AF%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%B2%20(%E0%A6%A1%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%97%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%B0%E0%A7%80)%20%E0%A6%AE%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%A6%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%B0%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%B8%E0%A6%BE|title=Dhipur Union|last=|first=|date=|website=Bangladesh National portal|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=3 November 2019}}</ref>\n\n== Academic Buildings ==\nThere are 5 two-storied buildings with 26 rooms, a computer lab, a science lab, 2 tube wells and 3 toilets in the madrasah.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://munshigonj24.com/2017/10/15/%E0%A6%9F%E0%A6%99%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%97%E0%A7%80%E0%A6%AC%E0%A6%BE%E0%A7%9C%E0%A7%80%E0%A6%A4%E0%A7%87-%E0%A6%AE%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%A6%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%B0%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%B8%E0%A6%BE-%E0%A6%AD%E0%A6%AC%E0%A6%A8/|title=\u099f\u0999\u09cd\u0997\u09c0\u09ac\u09be\u09a1\u09bc\u09c0\u09a4\u09c7 \u09ae\u09be\u09a6\u09cd\u09b0\u09be\u09b8\u09be \u09ad\u09ac\u09a8\u09c7\u09b0 \u0989\u09a6\u09cd\u09ac\u09cb\u09a7\u09a8|last=|first=|date=|website=\u09ae\u09c1\u09a8\u09cd\u09b8\u09bf\u0997\u099e\u09cd\u099c\u09c7\u09b0 \u0996\u09ac\u09b0 / \u09ae\u09c1\u09a8\u09cd\u09b8\u09bf\u0997\u099e\u09cd\u099c\u09e8\u09ea \u09a1\u099f \u0995\u09ae|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=3 November 2019}}</ref>\n\n== Education System ==\nUnder the Madrasa Education Board of Bangladesh, the students of the General department receive modern education along with religious education. The textbooks by the board were distributed among the students on January 1. In addition to the main educational activities, students take part in observing national days, discussion on various Islamic days and others co-education programs (painting, composition contests, ghazals, presenting national songs, etc.).\n\n== Teachers ==\nThere are 20 skilled, trained teachers to teach students.<ref name=\":0\" /> More teachers waiting to fill the vacancies.\n\n== Computer Lab ==\nThe Sheikh Russell Digital Lab <ref>{{Cite web|url=http://sheikhrusseldigitallab.gov.bd/lablist.php?district=%E0%A6%AE%E0%A7%81%E0%A6%A8%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%B8%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%97%E0%A6%9E%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%9C&sub_district=%E0%A6%9F%E0%A6%82%E0%A6%97%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%AC%E0%A6%BE%E0%A7%9C%E0%A7%80|title=Sheikh Russel Digital Lab Project|last=|first=|date=|website=sheikhrusseldigitallab.gov.bd|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=20 April 2020}}</ref> provided by the Government of Bangladesh is to make the students of the institution skilled in information technology. Here classes are conducted through multimedia so that students can understand and learn the lessons more attractively. There are also arrangements for admission to various computer learning courses for both institutional and external.\n\n== Result ==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n!#\n!Exam name\n!year\n!Passing rate\n|-\n|1\n|EEC\n|2018\n|100% <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://dpe.portal.gov.bd/sites/default/files/files/dpe.portal.gov.bd/files/46912b2c_5aa9_4c90_bfe1_6f29ac3818bb/312%20Munshigonj.pdf|title=\u0987\u09ac\u09a4\u09c7\u09a6\u09be\u09af\u09bc\u09c0 \u09b6\u09bf\u0995\u09cd\u09b7\u09be \u09b8\u09ae\u09be\u09aa\u09a8\u09c0 \u09ab\u09b2\u09be\u09ab\u09b2 \u09e8\u09e6\u09e7\u09ee (\u09b8\u0995\u09b2 \u099c\u09c7\u09b2\u09be)|last=|first=|date=|website=\u09aa\u09cd\u09b0\u09be\u09a5\u09ae\u09bf\u0995 \u09b6\u09bf\u0995\u09cd\u09b7\u09be \u0985\u09a7\u09bf\u09a6\u09aa\u09cd\u09a4\u09b0, \u0997\u09a3\u09aa\u09cd\u09b0\u099c\u09be\u09a4\u09a8\u09cd\u09a4\u09cd\u09b0\u09c0 \u09ac\u09be\u0982\u09b2\u09be\u09a6\u09c7\u09b6 \u09b8\u09b0\u0995\u09be\u09b0|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=3 November 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|2\n|JDC\n|2018\n|95.56% <ref name=\"eboardresults.com\">{{Cite web|url=https://eboardresults.com/app/stud/|title=WEB BASED RESULT|last=|first=|date=|website=Ministry of Education, Bangladesh|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=3 November 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|3\n|Dakhil\n|2019\n|80.77% <ref name=\"eboardresults.com\" />\n|-\n|4\n|Alim\n|2019\n|88.89% <ref name=\"eboardresults.com\" />\n|-\n|5\n|Fazil\n|2019\n|100% <ref>{{Cite web|url=http://result.iau.edu.bd/|title=\u09ab\u09be\u09af\u09bf\u09b2 \u09ab\u09b2\u09be\u09ab\u09b2|last=|first=|date=|website=\u0987\u09b8\u09b2\u09be\u09ae\u09bf \u0986\u09b0\u09ac\u09bf \u09ac\u09bf\u09b6\u09cd\u09ac\u09ac\u09bf\u09a6\u09cd\u09af\u09be\u09b2\u09af\u09bc|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=3 November 2019}}</ref>\n|}\n\n== Management Committee ==\nThe governing body of the Madrasa is a total of 15 members, including Engg. Qazi Abdul Wahid (president), Alhaj Abdul Sobhan Sheikh (vice-president), 3 electoral members and 9 members.\n\n== Volume ==\nThe total area of the institution is 2.22 acres.\n\n== Gallery ==\n{{Image frame|content=[[File:Dhipur Madrasah-panaroma.jpg|500px]]|width=500|align=center|caption=Views of Dhippur Islamia Fazil Madrasa, Tongbari, Munshiganj|max-width=}}\n{{Image frame|content=[[File:Dhipur Madrasah-3.jpg|160px]][[File:Dhipur Madrasah-1.jpg|160px]][[File:Dhipur Madrasah-2.jpg|160px]]|width=500|align=center|caption=Below are three pictures from the roof of the Dhipur Islamia Ideal Orphanage building|max-width=}}\n\n== See also ==\n* [[Madrasa|<span data-segmentid=\"121\" class=\"cx-segment ve-pasteProtect\"></span>]][[Madrasa]] [[Madrasa|<span data-segmentid=\"121\" class=\"cx-segment ve-pasteProtect\"></span>]]\n* [[Qawmi Madrasah|<span data-segmentid=\"125\" class=\"cx-segment ve-pasteProtect\"></span>]][[Qawmi Madrasah]][[Qawmi Madrasah|<span data-segmentid=\"125\" class=\"cx-segment ve-pasteProtect\"></span>]]\n* [[Government Madrasah-e-Alia]]\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n* [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qf4fOcH8hgE&list=UUkfUbUji0uigtLBW6JyHWcA&index=2/ Check out the display of students of Dhipur Islamia Fazil Madrasah on Independence Day]\n* [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fb6tOHGx56U&list=UUkfUbUji0uigtLBW6JyHWcA&index=3/ See the display of students of Dhipur Islamia Fazil Madrasah on Victory Day]\n* [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8iJ-N5q430c&list=UUkfUbUji0uigtLBW6Jy